# ProjectHub - Modern Project Management Solution

## Overview
ProjectHub is a powerful, intuitive project management platform designed to streamline team collaboration and task management. Built with modern web technologies, it offers a seamless experience for teams of all sizes to manage projects, track time, and communicate effectively.

