## Technical Stack

### Frontend
- React with TypeScript
- Zustand for state management
- TailwindCSS for styling
- Socket.io for real-time features
- React Router for navigation

### Backend
- Node.js/Express
- MongoDB for database
- JWT authentication
- WebSocket integration
- RESTful API architecture

## Security Features
- Secure authentication
- Role-based access control
- Data encryption
- Secure API endpoints
- Session management

## Target Users
- Project managers
- Development teams
- Remote work teams
- Freelancers
- Small to medium-sized businesses

ProjectHub combines modern design with powerful functionality to create an efficient, user-friendly project management experience. Whether you're managing a small team or coordinating multiple projects, ProjectHub provides the tools needed for successful project delivery.